        <h2>
            大学 中庸 论语的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2864861">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2864861/" class="title-link">能令人反复思考的漫画</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2864861"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/phoebewen/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u3114056-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/phoebewen/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">球童鞋</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-12-16"
      class="main-meta">2009-12-16 14:11:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2864861_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我们总是很难说服一个小孩子去静静地坐下来看一本大家典籍，但我们能很轻易地让一个小孩子全身心地投入到一本漫画之中。 阅读时能很轻易的进入，进入后仍能很深刻地反复思考的漫画书。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2864861_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2864861_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





